Thrifty is a Google Chrome Extension designed to make your life easier by searching for items across various classified ads platforms in Europe. The extension opens multiple tabs to find matching results for you. The amount of matching results are shown as well as the cheapest price.

Thrifty is an open source project which is maintained here: [https://github.com/emanuelschmitt/thrifty-chrome-extension](https://github.com/emanuelschmitt/thrifty-chrome-extension). Contributions are welcome to improve the extension.
